  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The shaman can speak with mammoths and any other megafauna or elephant creatures as if she were under the effects of&nbsp;speak with animals.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, the shaman gains a bonus on Handle Animal checks when dealing with those animals equal to half her shaman level.</p>\n<p>At 10th level, the shaman can affect one such animal within 30 feet as if she’d cast&nbsp;charm animal&nbsp;(Will negates).</p>\n<p>Whether or not the target succeeds at the saving throw, it can’t be the target of this hex again for 24 hours.</p>",
